               <hi rendition="#b"><hi rendition="#aq">318</hi></hi><hi rendition="#aq">,</hi><hi rendition="#rkd"><hi rendition="#aq">2</hi></hi> Stein] <hi rendition="#aq">nachtr.</hi>
               <hi rendition="#rkd">3 </hi>Proben] <hi rendition="#aq">aus</hi> Weinproben</p>
            <lb/>
            <p>
               <hi rendition="#aq">Terminus a quo: Ende</hi> 1812 (jetzo, Geburttag). <hi rendition="#b"><hi rendition="#aq">318</hi></hi><hi rendition="#aq">,</hi><hi rendition="#rkd"><hi rendition="#aq">7</hi></hi>
